1. process Chinese Txt: 
	1a. in word, choose "Wildcards" to replace all "?" to "^& " (a space after &): this step add space among all words: copy this word file back to txt.

	1b. replace all the Chinese punctuation Marks to English Marks.

	1c. remove "\"" marks and some other marks based on your need.

2. Differences between English & Chinese:
	2a. no space between Chinese word: add space
	2b. no CapitalLetters in Chinese, for making sentences: only start four words：
		"你", "我". "他/她" which mean "you", "I", "He/She": set CapitalLetters to these Chinese words.